ABOUT LOU

On 27 Apr 2025, $Lou debuted as the cutest dog on eth, instantly stealing hearts. The community united to back Lou, turning meme into a movement.

With 1 billion tokens fully circulating, liquidity burned, and 0% taxes, $Lou keeps it simple and fair. The focus is on empowering the community and driving momentum.

$Lou is led by a skilled team with a clear plan to go viral. A roadmap is in place to take Lou from meme coin to cultural icon, reaching the masses.
